{
  "stem": "162.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just thought about this the other day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What did my mother do for money all this time?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we ended up in a little apartment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at that time, the Joint had set up an office.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And everybody that was displaced or was looking for relatives, they wanted people to register.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my-- we went there, and we found my aunt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my mother in her excitement forgot to register.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went-- we went to my aunt first, and we connected with my aunt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And naturally, we were thrilled that she was alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We found out-- found out that my uncle was killed in Auschwitz, but she survived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we rented this apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were going to go back and re-register.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the meantime, my father, in the village that he was-- in the beginning, if you want to back track.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He joined-- it got too-- too scary and too dangerous for him to stay in the village, so he went into the woods and joined the partisans.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when the war ended, rejoined-- I guess, was it the Russian army or the Polish army?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know if they were together or what.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I can't remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But he came to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he tried to find my mother and me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somebody who knew us told him that they know that my mother is dead.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They are pretty sure that she was killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they think that I got out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And maybe he could find me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So my father goes on a pass, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, he comes to Berlin to find us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The first thing that happens to him, he gets mugged and robbed by Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They took all his money.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
